README BACKEND FILE
EcoFinds Backend

EcoFinds is a sustainable second-hand marketplace built to encourage responsible consumption by making it simple to buy and sell pre-owned items.
This backend powers core functionalities such as user authentication, product listings, browsing, cart management, and purchase history.

ğŸš€ Features

User Authentication: Register, login, and manage user profiles.

Product Listings (CRUD): Create, read, update, and delete products.

Search & Filtering: Browse listings with keyword search and category filtering.

Cart Management: Add/remove products from the cart.

Purchase History: Track previous purchases.

REST API: Provides endpoints for frontend (web/mobile) integration.

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

Backend Framework: Django/ FastAPI 

Database: postgreSQL

Authentication: JWT / Session-based

Language: Python

