âš™ï¸ Setup Instructions
1. Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ecofinds.git
cd ecofinds/backend

2. Create Virtual Environment & Install Dependencies
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # On macOS/Linux
venv\Scripts\activate      # On Windows

pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Configure Environment Variables
Create a .env file in the backend folder:

SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key
DATABASE_URL=mysql://username:password@localhost/ecofinds
DEBUG=True

5. Start the Backend Server
python run.py

ğŸ“¡ API Endpoints
User

POST /auth/register â†’ Register a new user

POST /auth/login â†’ Login and get token

GET /users/me â†’ Get current user profile

Products

POST /products/ â†’ Create new product

GET /products/ â†’ Get all products

GET /products/<id> â†’ Get product by ID

PUT /products/<id> â†’ Update product

DELETE /products/<id> â†’ Delete product

Cart

POST /cart/add â†’ Add product to cart

GET /cart/ â†’ View cart items

DELETE /cart/remove/<id> â†’ Remove item from cart

Purchases

GET /purchases/ â†’ View previous purchase

